OL,3,CUK data centres to be designated as
OL,4,C'critical infrastructure'
OL,6,FData centres in the UK are to be
OL,7,Fdesignated as critical national
OL,8,Finfrastructure in an effort to protect
OL,9,Fthem from cyber attacks or IT
OL,10,Fblackouts, the Government has said.
OL,12,FThe buildings store much of the data
OL,13,Fgenerated in the UK ` including photos
OL,14,Ftaken on smartphones, financial
OL,15,Finformation and NHS records.
