OL,3,CUK data centres to be designated as
OL,4,C'critical infrastructure'
OL,6,FBy now being categorised as Critical
OL,7,FNational Infrastructure (CNI), it
OL,8,Fmeans data centres will be on the same
OL,9,Ffooting as water, energy and emergency
OL,10,Fservice systems and therefore receive
OL,11,Fgreater government support to
OL,12,Fanticipate and recover from major
OL,13,Fincidents such as cyber-attacks,
OL,14,Foutages or environmental disasters.
