OL,3,CUK data centres to be designated as
OL,4,C'critical infrastructure'
OL,6,FThe Government said the move, which is
OL,7,Fthe first new CNI designation in
OL,8,Falmost a decade, will not only help
OL,9,Fprotect critical data infrastructure
OL,10,Fbut also provide businesses with
OL,11,Freassurance to help boost economic
OL,12,Fgrowth in an increasingly digital
OL,13,Fworld.
OL,15,FThe data centre industry already
OL,16,Fgenerates an estimated #4.6 billion a
OL,17,Fyear in revenues, and the UK is
OL,18,Fcurrently home to the highest number
OL,19,Fof data centres in western Europe.
