OL,3,CUK data centres to be designated as
OL,4,C'critical infrastructure'
OL,6,F"Data centres are the engines of
OL,7,Fmodern life, they power the digital
OL,8,Feconomy and keep our most personal
OL,9,Finformation safe," Technology
OL,10,FSecretary Peter Kyle said.
OL,12,F"Bringing data centres into the
OL,13,FCritical National Infrastructure
OL,14,Fregime will allow better co-ordination
OL,15,Fand co-operation with the Government
OL,16,Fagainst cyber criminals and unexpected
OL,17,Fevents."
