OL,3,CUK data centres to be designated as
OL,4,C'critical infrastructure'
OL,6,FThe move to give CNI status to the
OL,7,Fsector comes as the Government also
OL,8,Fwelcomed a proposed #3.75 billion
OL,9,Finvestment in creating Europe's
OL,10,Flargest data centre in Hertfordshire
OL,11,Fby data firm DC01UK, which it said
OL,12,Fwill create more than 700 jobs locally
OL,13,Fand support thousands more across the
OL,14,Fcountry.
