OL,4,C'critical infrastructure'
OL,6,F"The huge #3.75 billion private
OL,7,Finvestment announced today in
OL,8,FHertfordshire is a vote of confidence
OL,9,Fin those plans and a clear example of
OL,10,Fmy determination to ensure
OL,11,Ftechnological advancements are helping
OL,12,Fto grow our economy and create wealth
OL,13,Facross the country," Mr Kyle added.
OL,15,FEarlier this week, Amazon Web Services
OL,16,F(AWS) also announced plans to invest
OL,17,F#8 billion in the UK over the next
OL,18,Ffive years on building, operating and
OL,19,Fmaintaining data centres ` for which
OL,20,Fit is one of the world's biggest
OL,21,Fproviders.
